{"tid":956011,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"可愛到心臟痛！《與神同行》李德春4歲表演生氣皺鼻…網友：「世界上怎麼會有那麼可愛的生命體」","createTime":"2018-12-26T02:13:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-27T09:41:31.000Z","uid":9573,"like":17,"dislike":30,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"aef436c9c164103706b8430ebd55f189348faa7d","tid":956011,"uid":9573,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:13:05.000Z","msg":"韓國女演員金香起因人氣電影《與神同行》中「月值使者李德春」一角打開知名度。其實她早在2003年便以童星的身分出道，在演藝圈的資歷已長達15年之久，「解怨脈」朱志勳都要叫她一聲前輩了。近日，她受訪時被挖出小時候出演綜藝節目的畫面，當時她因為年紀太小不勝睡意，錄影錄到一半便背對鏡頭直接睡覺了，這個片段再度曝光後，網友們看到直呼「世界上怎麼會有那麼可愛的生命體」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/23/1701775-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F1701775-XXL.jpg&h=2d2a3fc2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲金香起4歲上節目畫面。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/23/1701774-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F1701774-XXL.jpg&h=b68f73ad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n金香起在4歲時曾出演國民MC劉在錫主持的節目，當時肉嘟嘟的她對著觀眾可愛地自我介紹：「我的名字叫做金香起，今年4歲。」因為當時被稱作是「CF精靈」的她，劉在錫也不忘CUE她擺出各種表情，其中生氣皺眉的表情，以及龐大車尾載貨空間，直接融化在場的所有人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/23/1701773-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F1701773-XXL.jpg&h=c2179a22&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲金香起生氣皺眉的模樣融化在場所有人。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YP7yg9H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYP7yg9H.png&h=06fbbc4f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n節目錄到後半，小香起突然眼神空洞地看向前方，彷彿下一秒就會睡著一樣，經過重新調校，輸出高達40.8kgm扭力，等鏡頭再次捕捉到她時，她已經不勝睡意轉過身睡著了，劉在錫也相當無奈的說「在我們聊天的時候，香起小朋友已經睡著了。」網友們看到紛紛轉發這個片段，表示「可愛到發瘋」、「好想打包回家」、「符合現今物流業講求的經濟原則！」、「連香起自己看了都會被可愛到心臟痛吧」、「人類版哈姆太郎」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/23/1701770-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F1701770-XXL.jpg&h=b58948d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▼▲金香起錄到一半睡著了。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2018/12/23/1701772-XXL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2018%2F12%2F23%2F1701772-XXL.jpg&h=59b2d64d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f475d29d635a0b897087c56585f8c2772b74e263","tid":956011,"uid":153497,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:33:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">經過重新調校，輸出高達40.8kgm扭力，</span>"},{"pid":"50307fb4cfe58f754d239949390f04a546c2584e","tid":956011,"uid":73722,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:41:35.000Z","msg":"其中生氣皺眉的表情，以及龐大車尾載貨空間，直接融化在場的所有人。"},{"pid":"16ecd9bac3cfda3bbf0a577904cf6bf9cf6bbe42","tid":956011,"uid":61300,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:47:58.000Z","msg":"我唔會再quote出來"},{"pid":"0d45b6ed0882a5360dbf7f854d84213cf40adebd","tid":956011,"uid":113626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:49:16.000Z","msg":"朱千雪 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af5473308a1d8dbddd08e5361811b67a44df6e4a","tid":956011,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:50:35.000Z","msg":"入嚟睇千雪<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bf3803f0679b904039538adde2ba6963a72f83d","tid":956011,"uid":170044,"like":10,"dislike":4,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:50:57.000Z","msg":"屌你老母咁都叫可愛<br />\n你試下推佢出印度有冇人肯姦佢先算啦"},{"pid":"dae9a3fe2e3af01154bb56e58d9082dcccb6229f","tid":956011,"uid":4957,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-26T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"連燈好兒 錢凱晴完勝佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ebeddcf2ca58fd712a2b3d52e6cf801130555cc3","tid":956011,"uid":76098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8bf3803f0